00:16:41,530 --> 00:16:43,200
RICHARD: OK, no,
clear away the debris.

324
00:16:43,270 --> 00:16:45,170
JEREMY:
No, I need to... Jesus!

325
00:16:45,170 --> 00:16:48,570
-That's part of eating it!
-It isn't part of eating it!
I haven't even begun.

326
00:16:48,640 --> 00:16:50,570
