00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:51,540
Cheat.

328
00:16:51,610 --> 00:16:54,080
♫ Only the crumbliest ♫

329
00:16:54,180 --> 00:16:55,780
♫ Flakiest chocolate ♫

330
00:16:55,850 --> 00:16:57,720
-Oh, God.
♫ Tastes like choc... ♫

