than the Focus.

454
00:24:36,540 --> 00:24:38,370
-Well, it is.
-It isn't.

455
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:41,110
-It is.
-No, it isn't.

456
00:24:41,180 --> 00:24:44,180
Look, I'm not saying this
is perfect, cos it isn't.

457
00:24:44,250 --> 00:24:47,410
