yobbish.
-A bit?!

463
00:24:59,670 --> 00:25:01,170
But, Hammond, look at this.

464
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:06,030
Oh, yeah, you're right.

465
00:25:06,110 --> 00:25:09,980
Half a century of Mustang
history, heritage and pride,

466
00:25:10,040 --> 00:25:14,780
